:: return home {"position":"500,700","size":"100,100"}
(text-colour:cyan)[''Bird'']<br>
You reason that the others each faced their own challenges, and return home to apologize.  The mouse was small enough to avoid the cat, and the sausage is the only one who could jump into the pot to season the meals.  You all live happily ever after.  <br>[[The end.->End]]


:: set it {"position":"1100,400","size":"100,100"}
(text-colour:cyan)[''Mouse'']<br>
You decide to set the table right away. After completing your task with time to spare you decide to take a nap anyway. 30 min pass and you wake up to delicious smelling dinner. <br>[[Scrumptious!->NextMorning]]


:: throw yourself {"position":"1800,400","size":"100,100"}
(text-colour:cyan)[''Sausage'']<br>
After a wonderful dinner from the previous night, the bird and the mouse are both very satisfied with their living situations. You all live in harmony happily ever after. <br>[[The end.->End]]


:: wait it out {"position":"1100,900","size":"100,100"}
(text-colour:cyan)[''Mouse'']<br>
Just waiting it out didn't seem to do you any favors. The bird, while attempting to cook burned down the house with you in it. You are now toast. <br>[[Yummy.->End]]


